	id_c ← alt_ws`filter! map… map! has… get… set… join? join2? ⁻¹uniq then⚓ ⁻¹ ∪! ∩! -! ?? *? +? ∪ ∩ ⊕ ‖ ⚓ -= += ? * + & | ∃ × ! -0 -1 -2 -3 -4 - 🔒 …`
